\fs20 \cf0 When you launch EVOLVE, you will see an Input Screen where you configure your experiments by selecting options and entering parameter values.  When finished, click on the Submit \{or Run\} button. EVOLVE performs the experiment and displays a graph to visualize different aspects of the results. You may modify the data that are graphed and export graphs to PDF image files.Input parameter values and numeric results are also exported to CSV files where they may be analyzed with spreadsheet or statistical software.\
